Company Description                    




                        Millennium Pacific Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, is primarily engaged in the research, development, manufacture, and sale of consumer electronic products. It offers GPS personal navigation devices, mobile Internet devices, and digital video recorders, as well as trades in and sells accessories or electronic products. The Company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.                     


